---
title: Double Bacon & Roast Pumpkin Risotto with Toasted Walnuts & Sage
description: This hearty bowl of risotto works its magic in the oven. With smokey bacon, loads of veggies and cheesy goodness, each bite is full of deliciousness. Top with golden almonds for extra crunch, and a squeeze of lemon for a zesty kick!
